%% TrustyAI Explainability - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>(manages ingress)
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>4443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Serving
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceLogger
    participant ModelServer as KServe/ModelMesh<br/>Model Server<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>(PVC/MariaDB/MinIO)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Monitoring

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Payload Consumption
    ModelMesh->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Store inference data<br/>Filesystem/JDBC/HTTP

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 2: KServe CloudEvent Payload Consumption
    KServe->>TrustyAI: CloudEvent (HTTP/8080)<br/>org.kubeflow.serving.inference.request<br/>org.kubeflow.serving.inference.response
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Store inference data<br/>Filesystem/JDBC/HTTP

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 3: Scheduled Fairness/Drift Metric Calculation
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read inference data<br/>(Quarkus Scheduler trigger)
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Inference dataset
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Calculate SPD, DIR,<br/>KS-Test, FourierMMD, Meanshift
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (4s interval)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir,<br/>drift metrics

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 4: Explainability Request (LIME/SHAP/CF)
    Client->>TrustyAI: POST /explainers/local/{algorithm}<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext<br/>Auth: delegated to operator
    TrustyAI->>ModelServer: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>KServe v2 Protocol<br/>8081/TCP plaintext
    ModelServer-->>TrustyAI: Inference results
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute LIME/SHAP/CF<br/>explanation
    TrustyAI-->>Client: Explanation response<br/>JSON

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 5: Fairness Metric Request
    Client->>TrustyAI: POST /metrics/group/fairness/spd<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read inference data
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Dataset
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Calculate SPD
    TrustyAI-->>Client: SPD result JSON
